Why did Monberg fear a threat
to national security?

15
00:01:18,880 --> 00:01:22,475
The Directorate of Prisons has
rejected your application.

16
00:01:22,640 --> 00:01:27,509
Why can't I see him?
-He refuses his medication.

17
00:01:27,680 --> 00:01:32,754
He would never just run away.
There has to be a reason.

18
