Why did your predecessor supress
information about the warning on terrorism?

27
00:02:20,720 --> 00:02:26,795
There was a risk of compromising
strategy in Afghanistan.

28
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:33,513
Frode had an agenda. He knew
Anne Dragsholm personally.

29
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:38,151
She felt that the army didn't take the
group's explanation seriously.

30
00:02:38,320 --> 00:02:41,995
She argued the case for a group of soldiers.

31
00:02:42,160 --> 00:02:45,914
The lawyer contacted me two days
before she was killed.

32
00:02:46,080 --> 00:02:51,916
Do you have the list of Team Aegir members?
We need to talk to someone in Raben's group.

33
00:03:22,640 --> 00:03:25,518
Can't you stop that racket?
We're doing our best.

34
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:30,959
He was attacked in his car and
wheeled down here in his wheelchair.

35
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:35,272
We saw the smoke,
but we couldn't put the fire out.

36
00:03:35,440 --> 00:03:38,557
Are there Sprinklers?
They've been turned off.

37
00:03:38,720 --> 00:03:44,909
The same with the security cameras.
Shortly before 17:00.

38
00:03:45,080 --> 00:03:48,868
