Raben? No idea what he was doing here.

60
00:06:21,880 --> 00:06:27,000
Because everything indicates it's the same
perpetrator as before.

61
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:31,790
And Sarah Lund has it all figured out?

62
00:06:31,960 --> 00:06:35,999
She's smart, I didn't know they
were coming here

63
00:06:36,160 --> 00:06:42,190
Would have been nice if you had.
Kodmani may still be involved.

64
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:47,309
I'm going to take Lund off
the case for several days.

65
00:06:48,480 --> 00:06:52,075
Why?
I know what I said yesterday.

66
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:56,233
But there are two good reasons
to keep her now.

67
00:06:56,400 --> 00:07:02,999
What she thinks about 'Faith Brother',
that Kodmani keeps talking about?

68
00:07:03,160 --> 00:07:06,311
We need to have a broader view, she gives it to us.

69
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:09,631
And what's the other reason?

70
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:14,920
Kodmani has agreed to an interrogation.
On one condition.

71
00:07:17,600 --> 00:07:21,195
You must meet Bjørn before the wedding.
It's a bad time now.

72
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:25,239
How about a cup of coffee?
We could get together

73
00:07:25,400 --> 00:07:28,472
Any news about Raben?
No.

74
00:07:28,640 --> 00:07:32,315
What about the rest of his group?
They should be questioned.

75
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:35,711
Lund!
It's fine for coffee this evening.

76
00:07:35,880 --> 00:07:40,670
I'll buy some cake.
I'm glad. I'll see you.

77
00:07:40,840 --> 00:07:45,072
The cake should be without nuts.
Bjørn can't tolerate nuts.

78
